{"tid":370500,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"汽車交流telegram 谷","createTime":"2017-08-23T05:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T00:55:44.000Z","uid":31921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35042257d7023b639205db0d028d9f06faf8fcbe","tid":370500,"uid":31921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T05:26:51.000Z","msg":"眼見好似無車谷<br />\n小弟開左個tg谷<br />\n希望可以交流下<br />\n<br />\n1. 零件 改車 整車 <br />\n2. 買賣車建議<br />\n3. 一般關於車既所有問題<br />\n4. 泊車地點 車位等等<br />\n5. 汽車美容<br />\n<br />\n太多野想交流 不能盡列 係關車既就隨便問隨便講<br />\n條件只有一個 不能過份hard sell 賣廣告要適可而止<br />\n如發現經想洗版即踢 此谷主要想各車主做交流<br />\n不限各車廠 隨便加入<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ca63c5beba3c0099adeb322604de9d7a4faec0","tid":370500,"uid":31921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372118e72cedb5531f05d7a181915a381c8ec3b5","tid":370500,"uid":53885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T00:55:44.000Z","msg":"無車入唔入得"}]}